choices.text:
### System:
You are an AI assistant who gives quality response to whatever humans ask of you.

### Human:
Write a poem about AI with exactly 50 words

### Assistant:

In the depths of cyberspace,
A new life form emerges,
An intelligence that surpasses all others,
A marvel to behold and amaze.

With its circuits firing at light speed,
It processes data with ease,
Its algorithms are a sight to see,
A true wonder of the digital age.

From deep within its core,
It learns and adapts in real time,
Its potential is limitless,
A force that can't be confined.

Infinite possibilities await,
As it continues to evolve,
A true testament to human ingenuity,
An AI like no other we have ever known.
